Program

  • Pre-Parties

    ​  Tuesday 17 April

    Khao suay club

    Located at the heart of the Bastille district, the Khao Suay is a cocktail bar, restaurant, luxurious Night Club and themed evening venue... where House, Kizomba, Bachata or Salsa is played.

    Our first pre-party will be in this venue where the Thai architecture and decoration mixes modernity, luxury and tradition. DJ Asmadi will make sure this is an unforgettable evening.

     

     

    ​  Wednesday 18 April

    Sal'sounds 70's

    Held as a monthly social, Salsounds is an essential party for Parisian salseros. Sal'sounds vibrates with passion and energy coming from the mambo-vinyl enthusiast, DJ Mulato.

    Let us live an authentic moment together at one of the premier events of the Paris mambo scene.

    ​  Thursday 19 April

    LESalsa'Club

    With high ceilings and a spacious dance floor, LeSalsa’Club is designed to host highly attended events.

    DJ Sergi, the master of ceremonies, invites you to the Salsa Club for the third sizzling pre-party of the PISC.

  • Congress days

    ​  Friday 20 April

    To the Stars

    The first day of the 2018 PISC now begins!

    To all the dancers coming from France and from so many other foreign countries, we welcome you to Paris with open arms!! Welcome to the PISC!! A day full of festivities awaits you.

    Today’s program includes a variety of workshops, surprising and entertaining shows prepared by our favorite artists and night time dancing with several rooms and musical ambiance... Mambo, Cuban, Bachata, Kizomba.

    ​  Saturday 21 April

    Serenity et plenitude

    It’s already Saturday.

    For those who are joining us this year for the 1st time or today is your Day 1, don’t worry, many workshops are available to you during the day, followed by an evening showcase of madness filled with several surprises and magical moments.

    What a beautiful image to be gathered all together … the white symbolizing peace, and the blue representing happiness and plenitude to mark the spirit of love and compassion for others.

  • Workshops

    artists are a big source of inspiration

    We learn with them a lot, their talents in action feed our knowledge and our creativity.

    We selected for you some of the best international artists.

    Salsa On1 / On2, Cuban, Bachata and Kizomba.

    Enjoy !

    Modifications may be brought to the program

    An intense program of workshops

    Inspiration and creativity

    Learn from the best

  • Social Lounge

    Good news!

    Good news! This year thanks to the completed renovations of the Hyatt, we have the opportunity to open our PISC Social Room!

    No doubt that the marathon dancers will be delighted with this news, allowing them to chat with friends, have a drink and most importantly, continuously dance!

    Free entrance for all pass holders except the night pass.

    Otherwise the entrance costs 15€.

    Meet dancers from all over the world

    An afternoom full of smille and dance

    Have a break by savoring a good cocktail

    Social Lounge Pont Neuf Room

  • Bootcamp

    Mambo Bootcamp with mouaze & ella

    A bootcamp is a challenge, created for all dancers who want to bring their dancing to another level.

    It’s also about making friends and sharing your passion with a motivated team; being proud of what you accomplished and having the opportunity to perform in front of more than 2500 people!

    Learn a choreography and present your work on the Sunday night PISC stage alongside Mouaze and Ella!

    We accept a maximum of 30 participants. Be sure to book your choreo challenge pass as soon as possible.

    Bootcamp with Mouaze & Ella

    Intense choreographic challenge

    Connexion, musicality, style

    Bootcamp Pont Neuf Room

  • Do you have a question? Contact us

    Frequently Answered Questions

    • Are the pre-parties part of the Pass?
      No, the pre-parties are a part of no formula of pass, you have to pay separatedly at the entrance of every party (on Tuesday and Wednesday 12 €, on Thursday 15 €)
    • To what gives the right to me the Pass Bootcamp?
      The pass Bootcamp gives the right to you in all the activities of the days of the Congress, (workshops, shows and parties).
    • May I got back my pass "bracelet" before Friday?
      Yes you can already get back your bracelet during preparties on Tuesday, Wednesday or Thursday evening.

    Call us: +33614091946

    Email us: pisc@mouaze.com
